{"tid":103260,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"洛杉磯出現首宗「超級細菌」感染","createTime":"2017-02-01T08:07:43.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-01T12:15:28.000Z","uid":73262,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ddfacb41461af2c2177e4c5f73caa821fb4fd1b1","tid":103260,"uid":73262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T08:07:43.000Z","msg":"去年美國賓夕凡尼亞州傳出有人感染「超級細菌」，抗生素的最後一道防線也無法抵禦。日前加州洛杉磯亦發現「超級細菌」的第一宗案例，調查人員認為可能是患者在出國旅行時被感染。目前加州出現感染病例後，令美國總共有6個州份出現「超級細菌」的感染病例。<br />\n<br />\n根據美國《洛杉磯時報》報道，洛杉磯公共衛生官員31日宣布，去年一名在洛杉磯逝世的病患，事後證實感染攜帶MCR-1基因的大腸桿菌。洛杉磯公共衛生急性傳染病科主任舒瓦茲(Benjamin Schwartz)表示，該病患者在亞洲感染大腸桿菌，但當時是因為別的原因逝世。<br />\n<a href=\"http://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/1483663/%E6%B4%9B%E6%9D%89%E7%A3%AF%E5%87%BA%E7%8F%BE%E9%A6%96%E5%AE%97%E3%80%8C%E8%B6%85%E7%B4%9A%E7%B4%B0%E8%8F%8C%E3%80%8D%E6%84%9F%E6%9F%93\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Finstantnews%2Fcurrent%2Farticle%2F1483663%2F%25E6%25B4%259B%25E6%259D%2589%25E7%25A3%25AF%25E5%2587%25BA%25E7%258F%25BE%25E9%25A6%2596%25E5%25AE%2597%25E3%2580%258C%25E8%25B6%2585%25E7%25B4%259A%25E7%25B4%25B0%25E8%258F%258C%25E3%2580%258D%25E6%2584%259F%25E6%259F%2593&d=W%2FrRVga79FgW6ojUxQ3KLb%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=ca99f16a\" target=\"_blank\">http://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/1483663/%E6%B4%9B%E6%9D%89%E7%A3%AF%E5%87%BA%E7%8F%BE%E9%A6%96%E5%AE%97%E3%80%8C%E8%B6%85%E7%B4%9A%E7%B4%B0%E8%8F%8C%E3%80%8D%E6%84%9F%E6%9F%93</a><br />\n<br />\n「超級細菌」攜帶MCR-1基因，能夠抵抗一種稱作「克痢黴素」（Colistin）的抗生素。「克痢黴素」被醫界視為是治療高度耐藥性細菌最後防線的抗生素之一。MCR-1基因最早在中國2015年11月被發現。"},{"pid":"70d37d5cca37aa3a0c6f03ef0c625ad89c547580","tid":103260,"uid":36964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T08:09:07.000Z","msg":"屌 真係支那搞出黎的禍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7c05f2529d70ea7ebea74e01a5f85013d687d4f","tid":103260,"uid":30487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T08:10:19.000Z","msg":"中國新人類嘅年代來臨了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d58ca76e9394822ccf32187dd7bbb11ea9ec761a","tid":103260,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T08:11:45.000Z","msg":"冚球剷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5dbc6857f05a28daead5a71bcccc3b3785a6063b","tid":103260,"uid":2485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T08:12:08.000Z","msg":"Plague Inc <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a6a0feae2daecead46b2187eaec489f1fe96ab2","tid":103260,"uid":57787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T08:14:00.000Z","msg":"中國或成最後的贏家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f42b31a98e5ed27641c21b3ba03e58785d7642ee","tid":103260,"uid":2247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T08:14:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2ebf2821ca4acb758bb3e2941fa39ab00cfff84","tid":103260,"uid":29625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T08:16:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屌 真係支那搞出黎的禍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n香港人少少病都lur醫生開抗生素<br />\n唔開好似蝕咗咁 開咗又亂咁停藥<br />\n咪同支那人一鳩樣"},{"pid":"cc0045b057415cfce4622f0d66265d1fe44dfda9","tid":103260,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T08:17:21.000Z","msg":"鄰國d生化武器根本仲恐怖過中東果班 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/de